		@H Additional Information @L
		This is the first very difficult mission of the campaign. It's still not in the level of a very hard custom map but suffice to say the campaign will ramp up from this point. Use every tool at your disposal to deal with challenges present. There are a lot of invasion points on the map, and it has high military activity. This map is one that has been changed more substantially than some of the others.  @L@L
		Try to use walls, bridges, and forts to funnel enemies into one or two points on the map where you can set up kill zones. Defending everywhere will likely lead to getting overwhelmed as your legions cannot respond to all places on the map quickly. @L@L
